data.meta_description: BLANCHE SANCHEZ de NAVARRE was born in the year 1177 in Pamplona, Navarra, Navarra, Spain, daughter of SANCHO GARCEZ VI de NAVARRE and SANCHA de CASTILE. She was married on July  1, 1199 in Chartres, Eure-et-Loire, Centre, France to THEOBALD III de CHAMPAGNE, they gave birth to 1 child. She died on March 14, 1229/30 in Chartres, Eure-et-Loire, Centre, France. This information is part of Ancestral Trails 2016 by Patti Lee Salter on Genealogy Online.
